channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Political Assassination Attempts I Have Known
Two key states to see massive GOP voter registration operation
item.description: Heritage Action for America, a Washington, DC-based 501c4, is launching a major voter-registration push in Georgia and Arizona, seeking to give conservatives the 'edge' they lost by in 2020.

item.title: Billionaire Bill Ackman Endorses Trump for President
item.description: Billionaire hedge fund manager Bill Ackman endorsed Donald Trump in the U.S. presidential race on Saturday. "I just endorsed him," Ackman posted on social media platform X after former President Trump was shot in the right ear during a campaign rally earlier Saturday. "But...

item.title: This Is What Happens When Media Pretends Everyone They Donâ€™t Like Is Hitler
Pennsylvania Trump rally attendee speaks on 'extremely lax' security measures after assassination attempt
item.description: An eyewitness from the rally in Butler, Pennsylvania, spoke out about the "extremely lax security" measures at former President Trump's rally following an assassination attempt.

item.title: Trump Leaves Hospital Following Assassination Attempt
item.description: Former President Donald Trump is out of the hospital following an apparent attempted assassination on his life at a Pennsylvania rally Saturday.

item.title: Nephew of Former Trump Physician Ronnie Jackson Wounded in Assassination Attempt on Donald Trump
RNC's Secret Service clash thrust back into spotlight after deadly Trump rally shooting
item.description: Security at the Republican National Convention could be back under scrutiny after an assassination attempt against former president Trump on Saturday night in Pennsylvania.

item.title: Witnesses: Secret Service 'Blew' Shooter's 'Head Off'
item.description: Secret Service agents took out the gunman who opened fire at former President Donald Trump's rally in Butler, Pennsylvania by shooting him in the head, witnesses are saying.

item.title: REPORTS: Trump Requested Heightened Security Resources from Secret Service For Weeks, Was Denied
Trump campaign, RNC to 'proceed with our convention' in aftermath of rally shooting
item.description: The Trump campaign and the Republican National Committee said the upcoming GOP convention will still take place despite a deadly shooting at the former president's Pennsylvania rally.

item.title: Trump Campaign, RNC Say Convention in Milwaukee Will 'Proceed'
item.description: Trump campaign, RNC say convention in Milwaukee will 'proceed' after rally shooting, Trump looks forward to joining.

item.title: DRAMATIC FOOTAGE: Moment Secret Service Takes Out Would-Be Trump Assassin
Trump rally shooting: Heart-stopping footage shows audience members noticing gunman before shots fired
item.description: Chilling footage shows the moments before a gunman began firing shots at former President Trump's on Saturday. Eyewitnesses noticed the gunman before the first shots were fired.

item.title: Photo Captures Bullet Whizzing Past Trump's Ear
item.description: A remarkable photo was posted to X purporting to show the bullet whizzing past the ear of presumptive Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump at his 6:15 p.m. ET shooting at his Butler, Pennsylvania, campaign rally Saturday night.
